---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import SEO from '../components/SEO.astro';
---

<Layout>
  <SEO
    slot="head"
    title="Modern Compass - Find Direction in Life's Key Moments | Personal Growth Framework"
    description="A framework for accelerating personal growth in Self, Trust, Character, and Relationships. Helping you navigate life with clarity, confidence, and intention. Free tools & monthly newsletter."
    canonical="https://themoderncompass.io"
    keywords="personal development, personal growth framework, life direction, self improvement, modern compass, character development, self awareness, trust building, relationship growth"
  />
  <!-- HERO -->
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="wrap">
      <h1 class="brand">Modern Compass</h1>
      <p class="lead">
        Helping you find direction in the moments that matter most.
      </p>
      <p class="sublead">
        Modern Compass is a framework for accelerating growth in Self, Trust, Character, and Relationships.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- WHAT IS MODERN COMPASS -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="wrap narrow">
      <h2 class="h">What Is Modern Compass?</h2>
      <p>
        There are a lot of great self-improvement books, yet many skew academic or abstract. Modern Compass is different.
        It is built around four clear directions that are simple to remember and deep enough to guide real progress.
        It becomes your compass for tracking growth. Each direction has four layers that build on each other.
      </p>

      <img
        src="/Modern%20Compass%20Layers.png"
        alt="Modern Compass layers graphic"
        class="layers-img"
      />

      <p class="sublead centered">
        Each direction builds in layers. Start with the foundation, then move down as each layer builds on the previous one.
      </p>

      <div class="grid">
        <div class="card">
          <h3 class="h3">Self</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Awareness</li>
            <li>Worth</li>
            <li>Confidence</li>
            <li>Control</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
          <h3 class="h3">Trust</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Tenets of Trust</li>
            <li>Trust in Humanity</li>
            <li>Informed Trust</li>
            <li>Profound Trust</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
          <h3 class="h3">Character</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Environmental</li>
            <li>Developed</li>
            <li>Authentic</li>
            <li>Transcending</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
          <h3 class="h3">Relationships</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Empathy</li>
            <li>Resonance</li>
            <li>Affinity</li>
            <li>Loyalty</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- WHY IT MATTERS -->
  <section class="section alt">
    <div class="wrap narrow">
      <h2 class="h">Why it matters</h2>
      <p>
        Life does not come with a map, and every choice pulls you somewhere. Without clarity you drift.
        With Modern Compass, you have a tool to orient yourself, test your decisions, and move with confidence.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- PROOF AND MOMENTUM -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="wrap narrow">
      <h2 class="h">Join the growing community</h2>
      <p>
        Over 100 subscribers receive monthly insights and get Break the Loop, a guided worksheet to help you get unstuck and build momentum.
        Additional tools like TimeOS and the Impulse Wallet are unlocked as a subscriber if you need more support moving forward.
      </p>
      <p style="margin-top: 16px;">
        <a href="/newsletter" style="color: #667eea; font-weight: 600; text-decoration: underline;">Join the newsletter</a> to get Break the Loop free.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CLOSING NOTE -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="wrap narrow">
      <h2 class="h">A personal note</h2>
      <p>
        I created Modern Compass because I have felt lost at different points in my life with little to give me direction.
        I am writing this for others who feel that way, whether you're just starting out, navigating a midlife pivot, or looking for clarity in any major transition.
        While this book is not about parenthood, I am also writing what I would want
        my daughters to have as they navigate life.
        As I close most of my newsletters and TikTok posts, alwaysâ€¦ follow your compass.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  /* Layout helpers */
  .wrap { max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 20px; }
  .wrap.narrow { max-width: 800px; }
  .section { padding: 56px 0; background: #ffffff; color: #111; }
  .section.alt { background: #f8fafc; }

  /* Hero */
  .hero { padding: 56px 0 40px; text-align: center; background: #ffffff; color: #111; }
  .brand {
    font-size: clamp(28px, 5vw, 48px);
    line-height: 1.1;
    margin: 0 0 8px 0;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    display: inline-block;
    background-image: var(--gradient, linear-gradient(45deg,
      var(--color-purple, #8b5cf6) 0%,
      var(--color-blue,   #3b82f6) 35%,
      var(--color-yellow, #facc15) 65%,
      var(--color-orange, #f97316) 100%));
    background-repeat: no-repeat;
    background-size: 100% 100%;
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    color: transparent;
  }
  .lead { font-size: 18px; margin: 0 0 6px 0; color: #222; }
  .sublead { font-size: 16px; margin: 0 0 18px 0; color: #444; }
  .sublead.centered { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 16px; }

  /* Content blocks */
  .h { font-size: 24px; margin: 0 0 12px 0; color: #111; }
  .h3 { font-size: 18px; margin: 0 0 4px 0; color: #111; }
  p { margin: 0 0 12px 0; color: #333; }

  .layers-img {
    display: block;
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 12px auto;
    height: auto;
  }
  .grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, minmax(0, 1fr));
    gap: 14px;
    margin-top: 12px;
  }
  .card {
    background: #ffffff;
    border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
    border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 14px;
  }
  .card ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding-left: 0;
    margin: 0;
  }
  .card li { margin-bottom: 4px; }

  /* Responsive */
  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr)); }
  }
  @media (max-width: 560px) {
    .grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }

  /* Optional: visually-hidden utility for the H2 inside the embed */
  .sr-only {
    position: absolute; width: 1px; height: 1px; padding: 0; margin: -1px;
    overflow: hidden; clip: rect(0,0,1px,1px); white-space: nowrap; border: 0;
  }
</style>
